mg_jungle_course
==================

Hello Guy's

Welcome to my second released map. This map is an "course" map, the objective is to get to the end without dying. This map should be build in jungle style but looks more like in a forrest. This map is build with Bees[Cz], but he quited becouse of he study's. This map is way different to other course maps, it isn't too long and not too hard.

What do the map contains?

	- Nice design.
	- Much detail.
	- Good lightning.
	- Some new traps.
	- Variation to other course maps.

Fixxe's
	
	- Fixed Spawn Proctection bug.


Hope you enjoy the map. Please rate and comment.
